                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It's easier than you think.
<br />

<br />
If you don't want to play it, don't play it.
<br />

<br />
If someone gets unnerved with you over any choices you take for yourself, **** them.
<br />

<br />
Pretty simple.  No need to have it drawn out and dragged along the ground.  Do what you want to do, and everyone else can fall to the side and be happy for you.
<br />

<br />
Now what I've been doing with a lot of my friends leaving for EQ2 or where ever is that I've been making new friends.  Yep, people are replaceable kinda like light bulbs.  Not being shallow, it's a fact.  Besides, I love meeting new people.  I think it's fun.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Bedazzler & Forest Stalker, Vadeanya & Zardak Zepiroth.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
